I have not desire being a Warrior.  However, in the mid 40's and definitely in the 50's as well as raid situation, Warriors are necessary.  <br>
<br>
I had a similar problem with my rogue getting groups on old server.  Once I got epic and over 50, I was in high demand.  Raids were dependent upon me.  Your time will come.  The SK and Paly are secondary tanks that in special situations are very vervy helpful (aggro control in NTOV ~ SK and DA pulling CT  ~ Paly come to mind).<br>
<br>
If you like the class, stick with it.  All classes are needed and us hybrids will have the tougher time in the end.  On this server, the nice thing is only one character per account so we just can't pull out our twink Warrior, Cleric, Rogue, etc.  Shamans may be the healers.  Paly may be MT.  Only class that actually 100% guarantee effects a raid in certain situations is a rogue (locked doors).<br>
